t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_569\" title=\"Chapter 569\">Next</a> →</td>\n\t\n\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n<b>Chapter 568</b> is titled \"Have It Your Way!\".\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Cover_Page\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cover Page</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Short_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Short Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Long_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Long Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quick_References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quick References</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Chapter_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chapter Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Characters\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Author_Comment\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Author Comment</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Site_Navigation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Site Navigation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cover_Page\">Cover Page</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_568%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hats</a> and Animals: <a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Zoro</a> is searching for a lion that blends in with the sunflowers.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Short_Summary\">Short Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_568%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Edward_Newgate\" title=\"Edward Newgate\">Whitebeard</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Marco\" title=\"Marco\">Marco</a>, and <a href=\"/wiki/Jozu\" title=\"Jozu\">Jozu</a> take damage from the admirals. <a href=\"/wiki/Portgas_D._Ace\" title=\"Portgas D. Ace\">Ace</a> recollects his hatred towards <a href=\"/wiki/Gol_D._Roger\" title=\"Gol D. Roger\">Roger</a> as well as questioning <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Garp\" title=\"Monkey D. Garp\">Garp</a> about whether or not he should have been born. In addition, he regains his will to live. <a href=\"/wiki/Buggy\" title=\"Buggy\">Buggy</a> and several other <a href=\"/wiki/Impel_Down\" title=\"Impel Down\">Impel Down</a> escapees remain stuck on a block of ice. <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> gets another dose of Tension Hormones from <a href=\"/wiki/Emporio_Ivankov\" title=\"Emporio Ivankov\">Ivankov</a> and re-enters the battle.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Long_Summary\">Long Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_568%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Edward_Newgate\" title=\"Edward Newgate\">Whitebeard</a> tells his allies not to be intimidated by Garp, as he is just an old man. <a href=\"/wiki/Sakazuki\" title=\"Sakazuki\">Akainu</a> reminds Whitebeard that they are of the same generation, then proceeds to fire a hound made of magma at Whitebeard, who deflects the attack and causes more damage to <a href=\"/wiki/Marineford\" title=\"Marineford\">Marineford</a>.\n</p><p>The pirates continue to cut a path through the Marine's forces, heavily damaging a <a href=\"/wiki/Pacifista\" title=\"Pacifista\">Pacifista</a> in the process. Ace suddenly begins to cry, as he recollects on his childhood; everyone with whom he had spoken about Roger despising the man, causing Ace to retaliate by beating them half to death. Ace had once asked Garp if he really should've been born; Garp replied by saying that was something that could only be discovered by living. Ace begins to loathe himself, stating that he's so happy that his allies care enough to spill blood for him that he cannot stop crying, and that he suddenly wants to live.\n</p><p>Meanwhile, <a href=\"/wiki/Buggy\" title=\"Buggy\">Buggy</a> and the escapees from Impel Down remain on a block of ice outside of the encircling wall. One of the pirates tells Buggy that he was thawed by the sea of magma. Buggy says to himself that he plans to take out vengeance against the Marines.\n</p><p>Suddenly, Whitebeard collapses, succumbing to the effects of old age. <a href=\"/wiki/Marco\" title=\"Marco\">Marco</a> rushes to protect him, but in his frenzy he is unable to foresee an attack by <a href=\"/wiki/Borsalino\" title=\"Borsalino\">Kizaru</a>, which pierces through him. <a href=\"/wiki/Jozu\" title=\"Jozu\">Jozu</a>, distracted by Kizaru's attack, has his arm frozen over by <a href=\"/wiki/Kuzan\" title=\"Kuzan\">Aokiji</a>. Akainu then deals a devastating magma-powered blow directly into Whitebeard's chest. <a href=\"/wiki/Emporio_Ivankov\" title=\"Emporio Ivankov\">Ivankov</a> berates the collapsed <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a>, who had asked for another dosage of Tension Hormones. Ivankov states that Luffy had been through too much over the course of Impel Down until now, and that pushing himself any further would mean throwing his life away. Luffy states that he will do whatever he can, even if he dies, as being unable to fight and failing to save Ace would make him want to die anyway. Ivankov reprimands Luffy, stating that if Luffy dies, then he would be unable to face <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Dragon\" title=\"Monkey D. Dragon\">Dragon</a> ever again; however, Ivankov tells Luffy that he can have it \"his own damned way\", injecting him with another shot of Tension Hormones. Empowered once more, Luffy stands up and lets out a scream of resolve.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quick_References\">Quick References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_568%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chapter_Notes\">Chapter Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_568%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D5&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>It is revealed that there are more people (other than Ace, <a href=\"/wiki/Squard\" title=\"Squard\">Squard</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Impel_Down\" title=\"Impel Down\">Impel Down</a>'s Level 6 prisoners) who hated <a href=\"/wiki/Gol_D._Roger\" title=\"Gol D. Roger\">Gol D. Roger</a>.</li>\n<li>The battle takes a turn for the worse for the Whitebeard Pirates as Whitebeard, Marco, and Jozu are all injured by the Marine admirals.</li>\n<li>Luffy re-enters the battle.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_568%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D6&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<dl><dd>first apparition</dd></dl>\n<table class=\"CharTable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Pirate\" title=\"Pirate\">Pirates</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Marines\" title=\"Marines\">Marines</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Revolutionary_Army\" title=\"Revolutionary Army\">Revolutionary Army</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Bandits\" title=\"Bandits\">Bandits</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hat Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Monkey D. Luffy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Roronoa Zoro</a> (cover)</li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Whitebeard_Pirates\" title=\"Whitebeard Pirates\">Whitebeard Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Edward_Newgate\" title=\"Edward Newgate\">Edward Newgate</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Portgas_D._Ace\" title=\"Portgas D. Ace\">Portgas D. Ace</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Marco\" title=\"Marco\">Marco</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Jozu\" title=\"Jozu\">Jozu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Vista\" title=\"Vista\">Vista</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Rakuyo\" title=\"Rakuyo\">Rakuyo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Curiel\" title=\"Curiel\">Curiel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Haruta\" title=\"Haruta\">Haruta</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Fossa\" title=\"Fossa\">Fossa</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Whitebeard_Pirates#Allies\" title=\"Whitebeard Pirates\">Whitebeard Alliance</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Buggy\" title=\"Buggy\">Buggy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Blondie\" title=\"Blondie\">Blondie</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Pavlik\" title=\"Pavlik\">Pavlik</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Rush\" title=\"Rush\">Rush</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Elmy\" title=\"Elmy\">Elmy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Jinbe\" title=\"Jinbe\">Jinbe</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Fleet_Admiral\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fleet Admiral\">Fleet Admiral</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Sengoku\" title=\"Sengoku\">Sengoku</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Admirals\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Admirals\">Admirals</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Borsalino\" title=\"Borsalino\">Kizaru</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sakazuki\" title=\"Sakazuki\">Akainu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Kuzan\" title=\"Kuzan\">Aokiji</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Vice_Admiral\" title=\"Vice Admiral\">Vice Admiral</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Garp\" title=\"Monkey D. Garp\">Monkey D. Garp</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt>Others</dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Pacifista\" title=\"Pacifista\">Pacifista</a> army</li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Emporio_Ivankov\" title=\"Emporio Ivankov\">Emporio Ivankov</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Dadan_Family\" title=\"Dadan Family\">Dadan Family</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Curly_Dadan\" title=\"Curly Dadan\">Curly Dadan</a> (flashback, hidden)</li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Author_Comment\">Author Comment</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_568%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D7&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><br />\n</p><table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin: auto; text-align: center; width:50%\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">Author Comment</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:90%\"><div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Translation\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Translation</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Original\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Original</a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p><br />\nI'm late in extending my thanks to Kosuke Kitajima and Aiko Kaito for helping support the movie.</p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p><br />\n申し遅れました世界の北島康介選手、皆藤愛子様の超強力宣伝協力に感謝です！</p></div></div>—<a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\">Eiichiro Oda</a></td><td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/a/ad/Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20230801133230\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Eiichiro Oda WSJ Avatar.png\" data-image-key=\"Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"><i>English translation by <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.thegrandline.com/odatocLIVE.htm\">Greg Werner</a>. For comprehensive translation credits, see <a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments#Translation_Credits\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">here</a>.</i></td></tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Site_Navigation\">Site Navigation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_568%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D8&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"toccolours\" style=\"margin:auto; text-align:center; width:80%;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left;\">\n<p><b>← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_567\" title=\"Chapter 567\">Previous Chapter</a></b>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\">\n<p><b><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_569\" title=\"Chapter 569\">Next Chapter</a> →</b>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"toccolours\" style=\"margin:auto; font-size:90%; clear:both; text-align:center; width:80%;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th class=\"cs SummitWarSagaColors\" style=\"\" colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/wiki/Marineford_Arc\" title=\"Marineford Arc\">Marineford Arc</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"cs SummitWarSagaColors\" style=\"\" colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Marineford_Arc_Chapters\" title=\"Category:Marineford Arc Chapters\">Manga Chapters</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_550\" title=\"Chapter 550\">550</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_551\" title=\"Chapter 551\">551</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_552\" title=\"Chapter 552\">552</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_553\" title=\"Chapter 553\">553</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_554\" title=\"Chapter 554\">554</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_555\" title=\"Chapter 555\">555</a>\n</